{
  "stem": "7093.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we were all ready, then we were led away in rows of five into another part of the camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we arrived at our destination, which was Birkenau B camp, called also Gypsy camp, which we didn't know at that time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know that Gypsies were also persecuted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Gypsy camp-- and that was a Gypsy camp, which was by that time already-- the Gypsies were already eliminated from that camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In this camp, there were only barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were about, I don't know how many barracks, and then there was a row of ditches.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then there was another row of barracks and another row of ditches.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a large square, not a tree or a blade of grass to be seen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Only electric-- electrified wire, barbed wire, German guards with guard dogs and watchtowers to be seen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Otherwise, nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In the barrack itself, there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was just a soil, the-- well, it was a sand, yellowish-greyish sand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that's-- and we fitted in, 1,200 of us, again, the same as we fitted in in the train, back-to-back and knee-to-knee.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we had latrines, which were guarded by SS men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Every time we went to the latrines, which we had to do very often.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because very, very soon, we had dysentery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Most of us had dysentery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were standing there and laughing and making jokes about us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In-- at night, if you wanted to-- I mean, when it got dark, they took us in to the-- put us into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And you were supposed to stay in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But you were allowed to come out if you needed to go to the latrine.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
